<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink308">
<l>palliruṅ kūntaṉ melliya lōḷvayiṟ</l>
<l>piriyā yāyiṉu naṉṟē viriyiṇark</l>
<l>kāleṟu ḻoḷvī tāaya</l>
<l>murukamar māmalai pirinteṉap pirimē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>It is better, if you do not part from the woman </l>
<l>of tender nature with thick, dark hair!  </l>
<l>You should part only after the dark mountain parts -</l> 
<l>the one where Murukan abides,</l>
<l>covered with bright floweres of Eṟuḻ tree,</l>
<l>whose trunk [is adorned] with opening flower-clusters.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
